浪费了占用空间了。 我现在想的是额外增加一个表，记录IP登录失败次数，登录时检查该IP的试错次数以及是否被锁定。 不知道知乎各位大佬有没有更好的解决方案，各位有什么好的解决办法吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Im5jJ5oWqrKwoEAMaCTEwOTQ2OTQxNCD0h/20BjAAODxADnIJNjYyMzYyNDc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"75 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8405179db9e611897742050eb05edc96_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1721967613.325297","card_id":"Q_662403528","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":662403528,"title":"今年浙江文科到底什么情况?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662403528","type":"question","created":1721745404,"answer_count":11,"follower_count":26,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[11171,213125,221843,602102,603829],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我是新高三学生。最近看到大批浙江文科生滑档的消息，我有点焦虑。特别看到很大一部分滑档的准备复读，我觉得这些学生也是很大的竞争对手。我已经不敢想2025浙江文科生，特别是像我这样的纯文的学生会怎么样。我的分数一直都在每次模考划的特控线上下，这会不会也受波及。想了解一下今年文科生录取的具体情况，实在是有点害怕。。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Im5jJ5oWqrKwoEAMaCTEwOTQ3ODU1MSD8//60BjAAOBpAD3IJNjYyNDAzNTI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"75 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1721967613.325798","card_id":"Q_662531306","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":662531306,"title":"如何评价《绝区零》1.0下半新角色朱鸢卡池流水表现？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662531306","type":"question","created":1721872960,"answer_count":21,"follower_count":22,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":""